## Performance Optimization

### DO:
- âœ… Use `--shard` for parallel execution on CI
- âœ… Install only needed browsers: `npx playwright install chromium --with-deps`
- âœ… Block analytics/ads: `--blocked-origins="*.analytics.com"`
- âœ… Use `fullyParallel: true` in config
- âœ… Cache `node_modules` and browsers on CI

### DON'T:
- âŒ Install all browsers on CI (wastes 5+ minutes)
- âŒ Record all traces (`trace: 'on'` - use `'on-first-retry'`)
- âŒ Use headed mode on CI (no display available)
- âŒ Screenshot every test (expensive, slow)

## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| "Browser not installed" | Run `npx playwright install --with-deps` |
| Flaky tests | Use web-first assertions, add explicit waits |
| Slow tests | Enable parallelism, mock slow APIs, use `--shard` |
| Tests fail on CI only | Check traces, ensure consistent environment |
| Healer agent not working | Requires VS Code v1.105+ (Insiders) |

